    "summary": "This section (\"数据描述\" / Data Description) on page 27 provides a quantitative overview of market performance from 2021 to 2025, structured around two key visualizations. It covers topics of annual market revenue scale and year-over-year growth rates. Dates span 2021–2025. Figures include a bar chart for revenue and a line chart for growth rates. Metrics detail revenue in billion RMB (36.48B in 2021, 35.08B in 2022, 34.72B in 2023, 36.10B in 2024, 36.46B in 2025) and YoY growth percentages (-3.82% for 2021–2022, -1.05% for 2022–2023, 3.98% for 2023–2024, 0.99% for 2024–2025). Claims indicate a revenue decline through 2023 followed by a recovery in 2024–2025. The evidence type consists of direct quantitative numerical data and chart-based visualizations for trend analysis and temporal comparison. No tables, definitions, procedures, or specific industry entities are specified."
