    "title": "图例",
    "page_range": "27",
    "summary": "This section provides a legend and source attribution for data visualizations analyzing the Hong Kong, Macau, and Taiwan mobile game market. It enables retrieval for questions regarding:\n- **Topics & Metrics:** Market revenue scale (in 100 million RMB), growth rate (%), and revenue concentration/share by game ranking tiers.\n- **Entities & Source:** 港澳台移动游戏市场 (HK/Macau/Taiwan mobile game market); data sourced from 点点数据 (proprietary research).\n- **Dates:** Annual data covering 2023, 2024, and 2025.\n- **Figure Definitions/Legend:** Blue bars represent revenue scale; cyan-green lines represent growth rate. A concentration chart uses color-coded segments: Blue (Top 1–10 games), Cyan (11–50), Green (51–200), Orange (Other games).\n- **Evidence Type:** Industry data visualizations (bar/line charts and segmented concentration charts) based on proprietary research.\n- **Retrieval Utility:** Answers queries on regional market size trends, growth trajectories, revenue distribution across ranking tiers, and chart legend interpretations."
